&lt;td align=&#34;left&#34;&gt;Boot mode switch&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td align=&#34;left&#34;&gt;Switch to change to boot mode.Press and hold the boot mode switch while writing a sketch.&lt;/td&gt;
