&lt;td align=&#34;left&#34;&gt;It is used for writing a sketch to the MCU and serial monitoring by connecting a PC.This also converts USB’s VBUS(5V) to 3.3V by using step-down power circuit and provide VBUS and 3.3V to each leaf.&lt;/td&gt;
